{"tid":896064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一男子突闖藍潔瑛追思會舉牌！「大佬出來謝罪」","createTime":"2018-11-09T16:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T06:05:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":169,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"6b083b45112ac7e1eb89af30122c2c37902c9da9","tid":896064,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-11-09/656/20181109004767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-11-09%2F656%2F20181109004767.jpg&h=df32dc1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一代女星「靚絕五台山」的藍潔瑛，在香港演藝圈紅極一時，可惜她晚景淒涼，本月3號被友人發現暴斃家中，享年55歲，她生前教友昨(9日在) 赤柱聖亞納堂為她舉行追思彌撒，李麗珍、鄧萃雯等女星皆有出席。但約莫下午6時許，突有一位自稱是大陸影迷代表的男子帶著許多劇照至會場外，還拿出一幅寫有「『大佬』出來謝罪」的紙牌，一度引起騷動。<br />\n<br />\n藍潔瑛追思會昨日舉行，吸引不少影迷到場致意，其中就有一位自稱是大陸影迷代表的男子突然舉著寫有「『大佬』出來謝罪」的牌子，稱要表達對大佬的憤怒，引發騷動，還吸引越來越多人一起舉牌。但這位男子就拒絕透露「大佬」說的是誰，只說「你們應該都清楚」，後來男子就被警察「請」出場外。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181110000022-260404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20181110000022-260404&d=J4Ft1hf15nuFqWWPUGG70zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=9c06c7ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181110000022-260404</a>"},{"pid":"008093db53ddb784347c42822bb5b7843f071c10","tid":896064,"uid":92178,"like":16,"dislike":171,"score":-155,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c1eae0823690c2cfdbab73eca3dc47380421028","tid":896064,"uid":73092,"like":87,"dislike":2,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"邊個大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b1241f31ab8de10c3cdd8f03d5c4e7c7225d11","tid":896064,"uid":23400,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"還死者一個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif